---
import Document from '../../layouts/document.astro';
import Hero from '../../components/Hero.astro';
import Section from '../../components/Section.astro';
import { frontmatter as indexFrontmatter } from '../../../../../docs/en/index.md';
import { useTranslations } from '../../i18n/translations.ts';

const t = useTranslations('en');
---

<Document title={t('index.title')}>
  <main>
    <Hero title={indexFrontmatter['title']} intro={indexFrontmatter['intro']}>
        <a
          class="nl-button nl-button--primary"
          href="https://github.com/nl-design-system/editor"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          {t('index.cta.github')}
        </a>
        <a
          class="nl-button nl-button--secondary"
          href="https://github.com/orgs/nl-design-system/projects/70/views/27"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noreferrer"
        >
          {t('index.cta.roadmap')}
        </a>
    </Hero>

    <Section>
      <clippy-editor id="clippy-editor-localhost">
        <div slot="content">
          <h1>NL Design System Editor heading 1</h1>
          <p>
            Among the cities that <strong>have</strong> <i>long</i> adorned the <strong><i>comital</i></strong> crown
            of Holland like so many precious gems, and whose power and wealth provided a firm support
            for the authority of the Count, Haarlem, as is well known, was one of the most important.
          </p>
          <h2>NL Design System Editor heading 2</h2>
          <p></p>
          <h4>That is not allowed</h4>
          <p>
            Built on the banks of a river of which it made use as
            <a href="https://example.com">two arms</a> to reach, on the one side, the Haarlemmermeer and the
            surrounding lands, and on the other the IJ, and through the IJ, the Zuiderzee, it had already early taken
            advantage of this favourable position to conduct a<a href="https://example.com"> </a>trade that,
            though seldom extending further than the regions surrounding those inland seas, nonetheless
            provided it with opportunity.
          </p>
          <table>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <th>Name</th>
                <th colspan="3">Description</th>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Row 1, cell 1</td>
                <td>Row 1, cell 2</td>
                <td>Row 1, cell 3</td>
                <td>Row 1, cell 4</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
          <dl>
            <dt>Foo</dt>
            <dd>The meaning of foo</dd>
            <dt>Bar</dt>
            <dd>The meaning of bar</dd>
          </dl>
          <h2>Images</h2>
          <img alt="Test size 800x400" src="https://placehold.co/800x400" />
          <h3>Correct list</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Test</li>
            <li>Test</li>
            <li>Test</li>
          </ul>
          <h3>Incorrect numbered list</h3>
          <p>1 - Test<br />2 - Test<br />3 - Test</p>
        </div>
      </clippy-editor>
    </Section>
  </main>
</Document>

